~find_star~END

[1]GAP.y=0 GAP.x=1
1(gap.x) = 2(i) - 1(tmp.x)
0(gap.y) = 0(j) - 0(tmp.y)
[2]GAP.y=0 GAP.x=1

~find_star~END
